
🐳 Docker Cheat Sheet
======================

📌 Docker CLI Basics
---------------------
docker --version              # Check Docker version
docker info                   # Show system-wide info
docker help                   # List Docker commands

📦 Images & Containers
------------------------
docker pull nginx                      # Download image from Docker Hub
docker images                          # List local images
docker rmi <image_id>                  # Remove image
docker run nginx                       # Run container
docker run -d nginx                    # Run in background (detached mode)
docker run -it ubuntu bash             # Interactive shell
docker ps                              # List running containers
docker ps -a                           # List all containers
docker stop <container_id>             # Stop container
docker start <container_id>            # Start stopped container
docker restart <container_id>          # Restart container
docker rm <container_id>               # Remove container

🛠️ Dockerfile Commands
------------------------
FROM ubuntu                            # Base image
RUN apt update && apt install -y nginx
COPY . /app                            # Copy files into image
WORKDIR /app                           # Set working dir
EXPOSE 80                              # Document exposed port
CMD ["nginx", "-g", "daemon off;"]     # Default command

docker build -t myapp .                # Build image from Dockerfile
docker run -p 8080:80 myapp            # Run with port mapping

🌐 Networking
--------------
docker network ls                      # List networks
docker network create my-net           # Create custom network
docker run --network my-net nginx      # Attach to network
docker run -p 8080:80 nginx            # Map container 80 to host 8080

📂 Volumes (Persistence)
--------------------------
docker volume create mydata
docker volume ls
docker run -v mydata:/data ubuntu
docker run -v $(pwd):/app nginx        # Bind mount current dir

🧩 Docker Compose
-------------------
# docker-compose.yml
version: "3"
services:
  web:
    image: nginx
    ports:
      - "8080:80"
  db:
    image: mysql
    environment:
      MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD: root

docker-compose up -d
docker-compose down
docker-compose ps
docker-compose logs

🛠️ Useful Commands
---------------------
docker exec -it <container> bash       # Shell inside container
docker logs <container>                # Show logs
docker cp file.txt <container>:/app    # Copy to container
docker inspect <container/image>       # Inspect details

🧹 Cleanup
------------
docker system prune                    # Remove all unused containers, networks, images
docker container prune                 # Remove stopped containers
docker image prune                     # Remove dangling images
docker volume prune                    # Remove unused volumes

🔐 Docker Hub Login & Push
----------------------------
docker login
docker tag myapp username/myapp:v1
docker push username/myapp:v1
docker pull username/myapp:v1
